<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
		<style></style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<div style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f5f5f5; color: #475467; max-width: 600px; margin: 20px auto; background-image: url('https://raw.githubusercontent.com/mosip/documentation/1.2.0/docs/_images/header_background.png'); border: 1px solid #e0e0e0; border-radius: 20px; padding: 0 2px 1rem 2px;" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="600">
			<div style="color: #ffffff; text-align: left; padding: 24px 36px;">
				<img style=" height: 58px; width: 150px; vertical-align: middle; margin-right: 10px;" src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/mosip/documentation/1.2.0/docs/_images/new_Mosip_logo.png" alt="Logo" />
			</div>
			<div style="padding: 20px 36px; line-height: 1.5; background-color: #ffffff;">
				<div style="font-size: 14px;">
					<p><strong>Dear ${partnerId},</strong></p>
					<p>This is to inform you that the Partner Certificate for ${partnerDomain} domain is scheduled to expire on ${expiryDateTime} UTC. To ensure continued functionality and uninterrupted services, we request you to upload the certificate for renewal before the expiration date.</p>
					<div style="padding: 10px 20px; background-color: #FAFBFC; border-radius: 10px;">
						<p style="font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold;">Certificate Details</p>
						<hr style="border-top: 1px solid #E5E5E5;"/>
						<p style="padding: 5px 0px; font-weight: 600;">Partner Domain<br><span style="font-weight: 400;">${partnerDomain}</span></P>
						<p style="padding: 5px 0px; font-weight: 600;">Expiration Date & Time<br><span style="font-weight: 400;">${expiryDateTime} UTC</span></P>
						<p style="padding: 5px 0px; font-weight: 600;">Issued To<br><span style="font-weight: 400;">${issuedTo}</span></P>
						<p style="padding: 5px 0px; font-weight: 600;">Issued By<br><span style="font-weight: 400;">${issuedBy}</span></P>
						<p style="padding: 5px 0px; font-weight: 600;">Action Required<br><span style="font-weight: 400;"> Upload the certificate for renewal in ‘Partner Certificate’.</span></P>
					</div>
					<p>Failure to renew the certificate before its expiration may result in service disruptions.</p>
					<p>To proceed with the renewal, please follow these steps:</p>
					<ol>
						<li>Log in to your account on the PMS Portal.</li>
						<li>Navigate to ‘Partner Certificate’ in Partner Dashboard and click on ‘Re-upload’ button.</li>
						<li>Upload the new certificate for renewal and complete the process.</li>
					</ol>
					<p>Please note that the expiry date and time are provided in UTC format, so kindly account for any time zone differences when planning your renewal.</p>
					<p>Thank you for your prompt attention to this matter.</p>
					<p>Best regards,<br>MOSIP</p>
					<p style="padding: 6px 0px;">** This is an auto-generated email. Please do not reply to this email. **</p>
					<p>Website: <a target="_blank" href="https://www.mosip.io">www.mosip.io</a></p>
					<hr style="border-top: 1px solid #edeef0;"/>
				</div>
				<div style="font-size: 14px; margin-top: 1.5rem;">
					<div style="margin: auto; border-collapse: collapse; text-align: center;">
						<a target="_blank" href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/mosip-project/posts/?feedView=all">
							<img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/mosip/documentation/1.2.0/docs/_images/linkedin.png" alt="linkedin" style="width: 24px; height: 24px; padding: 0px 4px;"/>
						</a>
						<a target="_blank" href="https://www.youtube.com/@mosip16">
							<img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/mosip/documentation/1.2.0/docs/_images/youtube.png" alt="youtube" style="width: 24px; height: 24px; padding: 0px 4px;"/>
						</a>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</body>
</html>
